----------------------------------------------------------------------
Third-party components
----------------------------------------------------------------------

Vuoom uses gifski (https://github.com/ImageOptim/gifski) for GIF encoding.
gifski is licensed under the AGPL-3.0-or-later. To keep Vuoom's own source
under the Apache-2.0 license, gifski is NOT linked into Vuoom; it is shipped
as a separate, unmodified binary and invoked as an external process (mere
aggregation). See docs/10-Licensing.md for the full rationale.

A complete, generated list of third-party dependencies and their licenses
will be produced with `cargo about` / `cargo deny` and bundled in the
installer and the in-app About → Licenses screen before release.
